Okay?

91
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,450
Kailangan ko ng oras.

92
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:34,050
Medyo nalilito ka rin siguro no?

93
00:08:37,920 --> 00:08:38,920
Hindi ba pwede...

94
